---
title: Creamy Lemon Cavatappi with Pork & Peas plus Lemony Breadcrumbs
description: Are you a lemon lover? Then this is your dish! You'll toss together springy cavatappi pasta with hearty ground pork and sweet green peas in a creamy sauce brightened with lemon juice and zest. Each plate is showered with buttery, lemony panko breadcrumbs for crunchy contrast.
